Titolo: Football Manager 2018

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Football Manager 2018 is a 2017 football management 
simulation video game developed by Sports Interactive and published by Sega  which was released worldwide on 10 November 2017 for Microsoft Windows, macOS and Linux. The Nintendo Switch version by Lab42 was released later, on 13 April 2018. For the first time in the series, all three versions of the game, FM 18 for PC, Mac and Linux, FM Touch 2018 for PC, Mac, Linux, iOS and Android, and Football Manager Mobile 2018 for iOS and Android were all released on the same day.